asreml.output

Class Slns

  • java.lang.Object
    • asreml.output.AsremlOutputFile
      • asreml.output.Slns

  • public class Slns
extends AsremlOutputFile
    Class to read in the Asreml Sln file which is a file that contains estimates for fixed and random effect with their standard errors in an array with four columns for the model that was run. The results are stored into a Map with the record index as the key and the Yht as the value.
    Author:
    Scott Smith
    See Also:
